<style>
    *{
		font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }
    
    a{
		text-decoration-line: none;
    }
    .btn{
		display: inline-block;
		font-weight: 400;
		text-align: center;
		white-space: nowrap;
		vertical-align: middle;
		-webkit-user-select: none;
		-moz-user-select: none;
		-ms-user-select: none;
		user-select: none;
		border: 1px solid transparent;
		padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
		border-radius: 0.25rem;
		transition: color 0.15s ease-in-out, background-color 0.15s ease-in-out, border-color 0.15s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.15s ease-in-out;
    }
    .rojo{
        background-color:  #C5313D;
        color: #fff;
    }

    table, th, td {
        border: 1px solid black;
        text-align: center;
    }
</style>

<div class="body">
    <center>
        <div class="container" style="padding: 5px;-webkit-box-shadow: 0px 2px 2px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.75);
        -moz-box-shadow: 0px 2px 2px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.75);
        box-shadow: 0px 2px 2px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.75); width: auto;">
            <img class="logo-mail" src="http://gafi.com.mx:8081/assets/login_logo-84d0085ea0e2611e7ad049152921cf004fdd6d1c15aa4542bb8ba98b8c8795f1.png" style="width: auto;" height="60">
            <hr>
            <div style="text-align: left; padding: 15px;">
                <p>Hola:</p>
                <p>Se ha generado una orden de servicio con la clave No.<strong><%= @service_order.n_orden %> </strong>. Favor de revisar para completar la compra de <%= @tipo %>.</p>
                <table class="table">
                    <tr style="background-color:#000000">
                        <th colspan="6" scope="colgroup" style="text-align: center; color:#FFFFFF">Información del vehículo</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="background-color:#BDC3C7">
                        <th scope="col">No. Económico</th>
                        <th scope="col">Tipo</th>
                        <th scope="col">Modelo</th>
                        <th scope="col">Año</th>
                        <th scope="col">Kilometraje</th>
                        <th scope="col">Responsable</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><%= @service_order.vehicle.numero_economico %></td>
                        <td><%= @service_order.vehicle.vehicle_type.descripcion %></td>
                        <td><%= @service_order.vehicle.catalog_brand.descripcion %></td>
                        <td><%= @service_order.vehicle.catalog_model.descripcion %></td>
                        <td><%= @km ? number_with_precision(@km.km_actual,precision: 2) : "N/A"%></td>
                        <td><%= @service_order.vehicle.responsable.nombre %></td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
                <br>
                <table class="table">
                    <tr style="background-color:#000000">
                        <th colspan="6" scope="colgroup" style="text-align: center;color:#FFFFFF">Descripción mantenimiento</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="6"><%= @service_order.descripcion %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="background-color:#BDC3C7">
                        <th colspan="1" scope="colgroup" style="text-align: center;">Proveedor autorizado</th>
                        
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td scope="col" style="text-align: center;"><%= @service_order.catalog_vendor_id ? @service_order.catalog_vendor.razonsocial : "N/A"%></td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
                <br>
                <table class="table">
                    <tr style="background-color:#000000">
                        <th colspan="6" scope="colgroup" style="text-align: center;color:#FFFFFF">Información del artículo</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="background-color:#BDC3C7">
                        <th scope="col">Medida</th>
                        <th scope="col">Modelo a utilizar</th>
                        <th scope="col">Cantidad</th>
                        <th scope="col">Precio</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><%= @service_order.catalog_tires_battery.medida %></td>
                        <td><%= @service_order.catalog_tires_battery.modelo %></td>
                        <td><%= @service_order.ticket_tire_battery.cantidad %></td>
                        <td><%= number_to_currency(@service_order.catalog_tires_battery.precio) %></td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align: left; padding: 15px;">
                <h6>Si recibiste este correo por error, por favor haga caso omiso.</h6>
                <h6>Este correo se envía automaticamente. Favor de no responder este correo.</h6>
            </div>
            <hr>
            <div align="right">
                Powered By: &nbsp;<img src="http://apbsoluciones.com/img/aeb45e_57da454c9def4d9d91c43503212fc73f_mv2.png" style="width: auto; display:inline-block; vertical-align: middle;" height="13">
                <br><br>
                </div>
            <div>
                <p><%= DateTime.now.year %> &copy; Gafi <a href="https://www.gafi.com.mx" class="m-link">www.gafi.com.mx</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </center>
</div>